final_queries: ['SELECT DISTINCT investor_id, investor_details FROM (SELECT LHS.amount_of_transaction AS amount_of_transaction, LHS.investor_id AS investor_id, LHS.n AS n, LHS.amount_of_transaction_other AS amount_of_transaction_other, LHS.investor_id_other AS investor_id_other, LHS.n_other AS n_other, RHS.investor_details AS investor_details FROM (SELECT * FROM (SELECT LHS.amount_of_transaction AS amount_of_transaction, LHS.investor_id AS investor_id, LHS.n AS n, RHS.amount_of_transaction AS amount_of_transaction_other, RHS.investor_id AS investor_id_other, RHS.n AS n_other FROM (SELECT amount_of_transaction, investor_id, COUNT() AS n FROM `transactions` GROUP BY amount_of_transaction, investor_id) AS LHS CROSS JOIN (SELECT amount_of_transaction, investor_id, COUNT() AS n FROM `transactions` GROUP BY amount_of_transaction, investor_id) AS RHS) WHERE (n > n_other)) AS LHS LEFT JOIN `investors` AS RHS ON (LHS.investor_id = RHS.investor_id)) ORDER BY investor_id']
